Rule	Spain	1949	only	-	Oct	 2	 1:00	0	-
Rule	Spain	1974	1975	-	Apr	Sat>=12	23:00	1:00	S
Rule	Spain	1974	1975	-	Oct	Sun>=1	 1:00	0	-
